replies.body:
Skarner doesn't need a kit revert, he just needs to get rid of the rocks. {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}

With the update his kit makes sense, is healthier, and works better together than it ever has; 
the only thing out of place is the Q (missing the phage-like ms boost).
Ditching the rocks and getting that Q ms back would do a lot to give the feel back 
(along with hopefully giving him back some of the base ms the spires stole.)
